high_descs: Turn left, walk towards the toilet, then turn right to face the bath tub.
Pick up the soap dispenser that is sitting on the rim of the bath tub.
Holding the dispenser, turn around 180 degrees to face the toilet.
Put the dispenser on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Put the soap dispenser on top of the toilet tank.

high_descs: Go left and stand in front of the bottle on the edge of the bath tub.
Pick up the bottle from the edge of the bath tub.
Go left and turn around to face the toilet.
Put the bottle on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a bottle on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Pick up the gold topped soap dispenser from the edge of the bathtub.
Take the soap dispenser to the tank of the toilet.
Set the dispenser on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Carry the soap dispenser from the edge of the bathtub and set it on top of the toilet tank.
